content.detailedDescription: I was in my car today and i ask my wife to get a picture of where i use to live in toledo, ohio.  she did, and the picture she brought up had the object in it.  i don't think the people who took the picture realise it'z there, because it's a realtor site.    my wife locked the picture in for we could look at it later, all i can say is wow!  i hope you contact me so i can send you the photo.
content.summary: It look like a saucer

content.detailedDescription: It was 4th of july weekend and the whole fam was outside lighting fireworks.. i was standing with my husband and talking to a cousin... i look behind us cause something caught my eye... there were no fireworks south of us, but saw a light. i stared at it for a while before getting my camera and telling my husband to look up, i started filming, but looked away from my phone cause another fam asked what i was filming, so i stopped the footage and showed him, idk if he saw it, or was just not into it, but he didn't seem to care, i've held on to this for a while, and i keep going back to it because it just didn't belong in the sky with all the fireworks... i've seen these before but this was the first time i was able to catch it on camera. thanks for reading :)
content.summary: Glowing sphere like object

content.altitude: 500 Feet or Less, Over 500 Feet (under cloudcover)
content.detailedDescription: My girlfriend and i were laying in bed after we had just got done making love. i was watching a college football game when out of the corner of my eye i noticed a bright flashing light flying lower that what an airplane should be flying. i live right next to the connelsville airport so planes and helicopters are very commonplace near my house, seeing multiple craft on a day to day basis. this was completely different and for the record both my girlfriend and i were completely and totally sober. there was two lights blinking together at first heading south southwest pulsating a white light and occasionally throwing in hints of green and orange. when i pointed it out to my girlfriend i turned off the tv turned off my fan and turned out the lights in my room and we opened the window and went and stood beside it so we could watch. well before she even saw the objects the one had completely stopped blinking so there was only one pulsating light as the craft turned and began heading south east instead. we watched the craft flying fairly low, well below the cloud cover, for between 5-10 minutes as it would occasionally stop and hover then continue on it's path. it was pulsating different color lighting alternating between white and orange and green but mostly white. there was absolutely no sound, and being that i live near an airport, i know as close as this object was if it were a helicopter or some conventional craft there'd be some sound. it travelled across the sky blinking the whole time without making a single sound. it was an oval shaped craft as best as i could tell weigh blinking lighting and of what i could see it looked to be much bigger than the single engine and other smaller aircrafts that fly out of connelsville. it slowly faded into the background as it kept traveling and i was getting ready to go outside while my girlfriend continued watching it. she then said it blinked 3 times right before completely disappearing from view. i personally have been interested in the ufo phenomenon for quite some time but i have never seen anything like this before in my life. feel free to check my story and contact me for a follow up and/or if you have questions
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Ufo spotted right outside my window. turned off all background noise and looked into the event

content.detailedDescription:
I was standing on my front porch looking up at the night sky when i observed what appeared to be at first sight two falling meteors falling straight down quickly at the same time with the same trajectory in the north east at about 60 degrees until about 30 to 25 degrees and then curved simultaneously in the same direction and disappeared. their approximate size was in between star-like and an aspirin with a yellowish orange color.
when i saw the two falling at the same time, i was excited and exclaimed " oh!! oh!!".
i am an avid sky watcher and have never quite observed anything quite like this.
content.summary: Seemed to be falling straight down simultainiously with curving direction change

content.detailedDescription: I am an electrician in fort mcmurray alberta    i was going out for a cigarette at exactly 907 pm ( iphone was in hand) i always look up just to check out stars / northern lights etc.  as i was staring almost straight up the object broke the edge of the roofline above my head and proceeded above cloud cover in a northerly direction.  it made exactly five course corrections at speeds far beyond anything i am aware of ( live near canadian afb see a lot of fighters etc.  ).  object was above light cloud cover and gave off a diffuse pale yellow light ( no smaller details visible .  the object then vanished over perceived horizon provided by town house across the backyard ( sub division ) the object went in and out of sight in approx 1.5 seconds so quickly it was comparable to at least 20 times the speed of a commercial jet.  as i have already timed a commercial flight at high altitude in relation to sighting and it was at least 23 seconds for the flight to come in and out of sight. speed and handling that was quite frankly awe inspiring. i have seen many things in the sky and this was with out a doubt an object we have no direct knowledge of under intelligent command. unreal experience. gave me butterflies and scared me half to death.  i am privileged to have seen it.  i have made a crude drawing of flight path etc and would be happy to forward.
content.summary: Directly overhead. above cloud cover. 1.5 seconds horizon to horizon ( perceived by structures) 5 course changes. at least 20x comm. air. speed.  dull yellow / 10 times airliner in diameter ( from perspective ) extremely extremely fast.

content.detailedDescription: was leaving my farm at 9:20 pm, as i was going to the gate i noticed very bright star were none. i got out of my truck and started an app on my phone to identify the star. according to the app there was no star there. verify gps and they were act object then shot up at a high rate of speed and disappeaed. the object was very bright and orange in color. it was 30° above the horizon.
content.summary: Observed a star in a place where there was none. then shot straight up.

content.detailedDescription: Fishing on saleen lake buckeye louisiana, man fishing with me said look that big plane is leaving a smoke trail the one behind it is not, i looked and it appeared to be cone shaped craft, then it shot off to rear of plane , this plane travels 700 mph, and it left it like speed of light, across sky, stoped and went in another direction. usa has a nice craft !
content.summary: Stainless metal ,oval, cylinder, behind a barksdale airforce bomber .

content.detailedDescription: My cousin and i were hunting deer in fall of 1983 park falls wisconsin, price county evening, dark out side, we were heading east back to park falls when we both noticed a very bright light ahead of us . we proceeded down the county highway and we are getting closer, and the light is getting bigger, now we are directly underneath the object and its really close to us 50 ft approximately. we were both shocked at what we were seeing. i pulled to the side of the road shut the truck off and just was amazed at what we were seeing. we were both scared but i could not just keep going i had to stop. we watched for 3 to 5 minutes it seemed like then it slowly just started moving to the west in the same direction we had just came from. in 1983 we had no cell phones cameras were not that advanced as they are now and we didn't have one. on our way home we talked about what had just happened and decided not to say any thing to anyone for the reason it was just to unbelievable, so we didn't hear of any other reports about this and kept silent for many years and only spoke of this between the two of us. mind you, we were just 19 or 20 years old at the time, but we both seen the same thing. we today still have no answer of what it was. i would like to add, after the fact, when we first seen the light it was 2 miles ahead of us prior to stopping.
content.summary: Very large , very bright . no sound just sitting low tree top level.

content.detailedDescription: It was friday morning at about seven am. i was waiting for the bus with my little sister. i turned away from the road and faced our house. behind the house i spotted a shiney bright cylinder in the sky. i instantly asked my sister, airplane or ufo? she answered ufo. we proceeded to look at it hover in the sky for about a minute. we heard to disant sound of helicopters. that's when the crafts light started to dim. i told her this was real if we saw a back helicopter and sure enought within second a back helicopter was abouve us. we faced the direction of the craft but it was gone before the helicopter was over the mountain. still looking in the sky we saw the helicopter head in the direction of the craft.
content.summary: Saw a shiny craft hovering in the sky. it stayed hovering for about a minute until the sound of a helicopter appeared. it dimmed out and was completely gone by the time the black helicopter came into sight.

content.detailedDescription: Cleaning bathrooms with co-worker at the rincon, puerto rico lighthouse at approximately 5:00 am on 05/16/15. co-worker saw dark object on surface of water and called my attention to it.  i thought it was the island of desecheo. co-worker pointed out that the island of desecheo was behind the object. the lighthouse beam was pulsing but all the other lights in the facility were out.  was using car headlight to illuminate the bathrooms.  when we shined the car headlights on the object, the object lit up with an unnaturally brilliant white light.  the lights that lit up were around the base of the disk and were round bulb-like.  extremely frightened.  got into car and drove to the guard station at the abandoned bonus nuclear plant because he is an armed guard. reported sighting to guard, but guard said it was probably a submarine.  left guard and drove back to the town of rincon around ten minutes later.  while passing the calypso bar which is around a quarter of a mile from the lighthouse,  we looked out towards the ocean and the object was still on the water, but its lights were off.  did not stop to observe it anymore.  that morning we reported to the municipality that the lights were out.  the electrician (who is my neighbor) reported that when he went to check the lights they were working normally. my co-worker took photos on his cell phone, but they did not come out well.  my co-worker moved to the us and i have lost contact with him.
content.summary: Object either floating on surface of ocean, hovering just above surface or slightly submerged.

content.detailedDescription: My neighbor was yelling my name from across the street in a panic, first thoughts was that he needs help, so i ran outside and was in a complete shock as to what i saw. there were hundreds of moving bright bluish white lights spread over the entire sky, slowly moving as a whole. the spread was really hard to calculate but it was at least 40-50 city blocks long. after realizing that this was real i ran and got my wife and kids to come see by this time there were a few cars pulled over and the neighbors started to come out and look up in shock. we all just watched in disbelief as they moved away as a squadron like formation and got higher and harder to see until they were completely gone. my neighbor had his camera and showed me what he got, it was a bit blury, hand held sky photos are always blurred abit, but you can get an idea of what we saw. the photo is just a quarter or less of what we all saw spread across the sky., then i went in and grabbed my camera and tripod to try to get something cleaner but by this time the orbs were flying in every direction getting duller and harder to see, i managed to capture some very strange stuff in the pics attached.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering,Other
content.summary: Hundreds of blue glowing star like orbs

content.detailedDescription: In the early morning hours of october 15th, about 3 o'clock myself and a friend was substituting a buddy's paper route in thornville ohio. when we was only about 30 minutes into the route, on ridenour rd, my friend was observing something out the passenger window. the next thing i know, he says " stop the car". he had a very serious demeanor so i did. he continued to stare out the window, without saying anything. i kept looking but was unable to see anything from the driver seat. so 3:30 in the morning and on a back country road i put the car in park an stepped out. soon as i did i see what my friend was looking at. off not too far off in the distance maybe 150 yards away was an oval shaped object  with red white and green lights on the bottom of the craft from four  points flashing in randomized order. also one each side of the craft werea wings, looked what was attached by some sort of metal beam or rod, and the wings were not the typical kind of wings you would see on a plane, they were curved, almost in a u shape. the craft was ascending into the sky.  neither of us seen it on the ground, just from the point of ascension. once it reached its maximum altitude of 250 to 300 feet at the most, it began to hover for a few seconds. then it proceeded to move in our direction at a very slow pace. the craft was completely silent. it made no noise or left any traces in the air behind it. when it had finally reached the road and it was about 300 feet directly above us. the size of the craft was about a football field in length and in diameter. the bottom of the craft was shiny. while both of us stared up at this in shock and amazement, a 5th center light illuminated purple. either of us were to much in awe to move. it then continued its path in the direction it was going. never gaining speed or altitude. it was at this point my friend told me to grab my camera, and i took 2 still shots and 3 couple second video's. we continued to watch it till it was out of site. we than got back in the vehicle and continued the route, in the direction it was traveling but never saw it again. the rest of the night we talked about what we had seen, still in shock and disbelief. it wasn't until the next morning did we remember to check our pictures. and than we seen what we had captured
content.summary: While substituting our friends paper route, myself and a buddy witnessed an unidentified lighted silent craft in the sky

content.detailedDescription:
Montréal, le 23 septembre 2015 - 18h35

je marchais sur la rue fleury vers l'ouest quand soudainement, j'ai aperçu, à l'angle de la rue waverly, un immense objet volant non identifié, stationnaire juste au dessus des maisons, de forme ovale gris avec trois lumières blanches rondes au centre.
puis, il s'est déplacé lentement vers le nord pour disparaître.

js
content.summary: Objet volant non identifié stationnaire de forme ovale gris avec trois lumières rondes au milieu

content.detailedDescription: Was in my back yard just playing with my cell phone camera filming the moon when i got a gimps of this thing coming over my yard. i was not verry steddy with the video but i got a couple of stills off the video
content.summary: It flew over the back yard

content.detailedDescription:
I was sitting out side about 9:30 weds night 10/14/15 looking up to the west, out of no where like it just uncloak, this huge bommerrage shape going from north to south it was further then b52 fly, it was the bigges thing i seen up there, forabout 5 sec. it moved slow i could see it no light nothing 
 it looked grey, light brown, then it slowly went like it recloaked, it was
gone. also it was way out there in space, not close but far away, it was huge
 to me it could have been the mother ship
content.summary: It was huge bommerrag it look like it uncloak 5 sce than recloaked never seen that big of and objest like that one

content.detailedDescription: Had just moved into a new apartment complex in bothell, wa. the place was still under construction and this sighting took place during the afternoon on a friday. we were in the last occupied building that was complete and the sighting lasted well over the weekend. my wife and i saw a blue sphere gliding i would guess about 5 to 700 ft above our heads heading west out over the sound. then we were visited by four greenish brown orbs above the tree tops. i saw what resembled a christmas ornament that goes on top of the tree, pure silver to chrome in color. the ship that i am uploading i like to call the mother ship because while we witnessed all the orbs and others she stayed high above us and at about a 75 degree angle to our sight the whole time. my wife prior to this had not witnessed anything except what i showed her on video. talk about excited. that weekend really changed our lives because we feel they put on a show for us. we had just arrived in bothell for me to start a new job in richmond and it was their way of welcoming us to washington.
content.summary: Star like object in daylight almost overhead

content.detailedDescription: Looking out of my bedroom window sky watching and observing the planets in the western sky this time of year noticed a light in long distance that should not have been there. through 20x200 binoculars light was changing colors and appeared to be spinning. the colors were outrageous and the movement which appeared to be bobbing up and down blew me away. i had been keeping watch on this part of the sky because of the planets which as months pass will junction and pass one another. so i know this light was not supposed to be there. the light after watching and filming for some time simply faded away. has not returned to area since. another person saw it too and uploaded to you tube. when ever i am rewarded with a sighting i always feel lucky enough to have been watching for any event in our skies.
content.summary: Strange multi-colored light seemed to be spinning and slightly bobbimg in night sky

content.detailedDescription:
Was outside at about 10:30 pm and noticed in the far ne sky flashing red, white & blue lights. i live about 20 miles ne of chicago's o'hare airport so seeing planes in the sky is a very common site, esp. when they're in a holding pattern. but airplanes have clear, green and red lights. what i seen looked like police car lights. i thought that was kind of odd to see red, white & blue flashing lights in the sky. i thought maybe it was a "lifeline" helicopter but never heard any rotor blade "beats" in the air. whatever the object was it traveled from the ne to se horizon in a few minutes...Just straightline. 

i've been searching the web for aircraft lighting and never read yet mention of red, white & blue lights...Don't know what i saw...Just kind of odd.
content.summary: Flashing red, white & blue lights

content.detailedDescription: Object silver in appearance moving quicker than planes moving nw to sw and suddenly disappeared.  no cloud coverage.
content.summary: Solver object moving quickly nw to sw.  faster than planes in the air.  no trail like planes.

content.detailedDescription: The ufo sighting happened while i was watching the bhs soccer game. out of nowhere, a purple light appeared from the sky and caught my attention. a couple other spectators saw the ufo also. when i first saw it, i thought it was a drone, but as i watched it, i noticed it didn't have an ipad or anything connected to it, and it didn't go in any certain pattern of movement. the ufo also slowly rotated counter-clockwise. i quickly took out my phone and got a picture of it. the ufo hovered just outside the field flying in circles and going back and forth, while it rotated. the ufo also went low to the ground at one point. i hovered there for a couple minutes before rising back up into the air. i lost sight of it after about 20-30 minutes when it flew away from my direction and disappeared behind some trees.
content.summary: Happened while watching soccer game. hovered above field for several minutes then abruptly left

content.detailedDescription: We were staying at a motel in edmonds for the night and i am an avid sky watcher. i was looking west out of picture window out towards the puget sound and noticed a pretty bright array of lights coming in over the sound. i quickly grabbed my sony camcorder which i take everywhere and started shooting. the object came in first looks like headed east. then it turned towards me heading south. i zoomed in and it turned again towards the west and disappeared over the motel roof line. all the while i listened for an engine and there was none.
content.summary: Object with unusual array of lights and no sound

content.detailedDescription:
possible ufo sighting on october 11, 2015 at about 10:30 pm

this email was sent to tom wertman at 11:03 pm on 10/11/15.
_________________________________________________________________________
tom,
 
sharon was looking out our bedroom window about 15 minutes ago and she said she saw a ufo. i looked at it and i think it may be a ufo bit i’m not sure.
 
it is small looking, about the size of a large star, and it is not very bright. i went outside to look at it and i could see it sometimes. when i went to the front of our house there was more ambient light and i couldn’t really see it.
 
we have a venetian blind on the window and it is down but it is open. we believe the light is moving around but it is staying in one small area of the sky. in other words it hasn’t moved from the south to the east in the sky and the angle of azimuth hasn’t changed by more than say 5 degrees. a venetian blind has strings that run vertically. i moved my head so that the ufo was between 2 vertical strings. it appeared that the ufo moved outside the strings. i looked at it in relation to 2 of the horizontal slats and again the ufo appears to be moving up and down. i’m not sure if i am holding my head steady enough or if the apparent movement of the ufo might be from me moving my head slightly but not by my own volition. what it reminds me of is a flying kite that is pretty much staying in the same spot but just moving around randomly. the brightness of the ufo changes randomly too. 
 
i am looking approximately to the south (almost directly south compared to north main st. the azimuth is about 25 degrees. i just looked again and it is still there. we’ve seen it for 28 minutes. i know my camera won’t see anything if i take a picture. is there anything we can do to get some more convincing information that it is a ufo? i don’t even know if you’re awake and on line but i hope so.
 
pat shriver


__________________________________________________________________

10/17/15

by looking at the street map and estimating the angle north main makes with true south (15 degrees) and estimating the angle the ufo was from parallel to south main (4 degrees) the ufo was about 19 degrees west of south. the ufo was circular in shape. what we were seeing was not scintillation or twinkling of a star. i went outside and looked at the ufo without looking through any glass so the ufo wasn’t a reflection of light. our address is 1161 north main st. north canton, ohio 44720. there was nothing near the ufo in the sky such as tree branch or an antenna so i couldn’t estimate the distance along the ground that the ufo was from our address. sharon shriver is my wife.

when viewing the ufo we were fairly confident that the ufo was an unidentified flying object and not a plane, helicopter, satellite, or a planet. we were not 100% certain it was a ufo and would like mufon to check to see if it made sense that it was something that could be explained.

after watching the ufo for 30 minutes we quit watching it and went to bed. it was still visible when we quit watching it.
content.summary: Saw a small light in the sky that was moving slightly in random directions for a period of one half hour.

content.detailedDescription: [link moved to fi section/cms/tg]
content.summary: See link. this link and the newspaper clipping, isn't the best experience

content.detailedDescription: We were having dinner at a local restaurant. can't really give a detailed description as i didn't see this with my naked eye. when i took the photo, i was trying to capture the moon as i found it to be pretty that night. later when i looked at the photo i saw something besides the the moon in it.
content.summary: We were dining at a local restaurant and while waiting for the dining party to exit the restaurant i took a picture of the moon. never saw the object until later when i noticed whatever this is in the photo. it could be nothing, but i found it interesting

content.detailedDescription: I am an amateur astronomer and was looking up at night sky 15 september 2015 at 12.30 am noticed patch of grey light moving south to north. craft appeared boomarang shaped outline was dull grey and appeared to have static electric type outline. at zenith it sharply turned and moved to west continued then moved in north direction and appeared to have descended as it was larger. as it moved a funnel of light appeared, then a bright beam emerged towards my direction it appeared to have been from a triangular opening on the side of the outline of the craft the beam and funnel were visible only for a second or so the craft continued north over a lake, seemed to shimmer in the atmosphere, then appeared to be two grey disks moving north, one following the other then moved out of sight. the whole episode lasted for only 12 seconds or so.There was absolutely no sound made during sighting. object initially was high in altitude then descended, i was unable to judge distance but perhaps a couple of kilometers away.
content.summary: Boomarang object descends and emits light beam, changes shape.

content.detailedDescription: I went to lay down around 5:30-6 am in the morning when i turned over in bed towards the window there was an extremely bright light shining through. i thought it was a bit strange so i got up and investigated it and i noticed a craft of some sort just hovering there. there was also another smaller one just below it. the craft would sort of change in color and look. it had a reddish/orange glow and a white light on the bottom. the lights would change in brightness every so often. i was really creeped out so i called my parents into the room and they saw it too. it hovered around for about an hour then slowly ascended to where i couldn't see it anymore. i looked again tonight and it is back and it looks even closer. the white light on the bottom brightened up for a second then it dimmed a little. the crafts almost look like sail boats.
content.summary: First seen 10/16 seen again 10/17 at 6am

content.detailedDescription:
Travelling north west on holyhead road just outside shrewsbury shropshire uk, and had to pull over at closed garage called four crosses garage to check humming noise i thought was coming from my vehicle. got out of car and humming sound coming from sky and when looked up a huge structured black triangle was in the sky moving real slow to the north west. first thought it was a jet aircrafts aircraft maybe landing but no airbase or airfield nearby, plus it had no.Clear engine noise. it was approx more than 500ft by 500ft and was dark and solid but had a faint white beam projecting down onto the roadside and then the fields. it made a weird humming sound that was like an electricity substation but much louder. my wife who was with me said that it looked like it was quite thick and heavy as it moved. we watched it for about 2 minutes as it moved off over the fields. it then seemed to turn left to the west where it seemed to gain height. the white light flicked out then it shot off quickly to the west with no extra sound.
i have never seen anything like this before and it was definately note a helicopter or fighter jet. it moved like it was being controlled and it was no way a blimp or balloon. just before we set off on our journey a helicopter appeared from the north east and flew low behind the four crosses pub and garage. at first it flew across the fields but then circled us and it was clear that it was an apache attack helicopter. it then flew off to the west.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Huge structured black triangle

content.detailedDescription:
After observing the object in the sky on sept 26th(case #71599), i have been paying close attention to the sky. i was walking out to my car, looked up and again at 5:30am in the same exact location on october 6th 2015, i seen the bright light once again. it was different this time, it was pulsating, would get really bright and disappear. at one point it flickered, like something else was moving in front of it. 

as i video taped this object, it wasnt until i put it on my laptop to get a closer look, i noticed 2 more objects in close proximity of the pulsating light. in one of the videos i'm up loading, you cant really notice the 2nd object until it takes off toward the left of the screen. the other object is below the pulsating light, and takes off heading back toward the ground.

i am uploading the original video clips and video clips that i lightened/brightened to enhance visibility. i am by no means a video editor, this was the first time i have ever tried uploading anything to do with video. for the people that do know how to work with video, maybe you could dissect the footage and make these clearer or clean up the pixalation!

i am going to continue to watch the sky, and try to capture whatever i can. i'm still in disbelief it happened same time of day, in the same location a few weeks later.
content.summary: Pulsating object with 2 other objects in video for short time

content.detailedDescription:
On sept 26th at 5:30am walked out to my car to grab something and immediately noticed a super bright light at the top of the tree line. at first i thought it was an airplane's headlight. stood and watched it for a few minutes and noticed it wasn't moving. for a brief moment i considered it might be a planet, until i realized wispy clouds were moving behind it.

i ran and grabbed my cell phone to video tape it. i ended up sitting in the road for 2 1/2 hours filming this object. i sat my phone on the asphalt and propped it up to avoid movement/shaking during filming. i heard helicopters when i first started filming, but couldn't see them. i can produce all original videos.

during this time it was a very clear night with the exception of a few wispy clouds. stars were visible, and this is not a star or a planet! my cell phone would only tape in 28min intervals. for the first 15min the object moved at a steady pace toward the south east while ascending higher in the sky. after 16min i had to move out of the road and when i was able to focus back onto this object there was a second object on the same horizontal plane as the bright light. watch the video!! the second object i couldn't see with my own eyes in the sky, i could only see it on my screen. whatever it is, it is rotating at a high rate of speed and looked transparent but could be seen because of how bright the other object was it was giving off a reflection. i filmed the 2 objects for almost 4 minutes until i had to move out of the road because a car was coming. when i focused back on the area the transparent looking object was gone.

the bright light seemed to hold its position for about an hour, then slowly, very slowly moved toward south west while ascending higher in the sky. the sun started coming up and still could see the object. by 8:30am i gave up on watching and waiting for something else to happen.
content.summary: Bright object at first, then second object appeared next to bright object
